folder: Gouverneur Street & Front Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
View 1;
Gouverneur Street, Front to South Street,
showing R.A. piers of the N.Y. and New
Haven R.R.

View 2;
Gouverneur Street; from Water Street,
looking north showing clearing between
Cherry and Monroe Street.

P.L.Speer/
NO REPRODUCTION.                     September 18, 1939.
